and high speed flow computations. Numerical results validate the\noutstanding reliability and applicability of the scheme for three-dimensional\nflows, such as turbulent one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jan 2018 13:47:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
